WEBVTT

00:01:58.800 --> 00:02:00.236
ga na-eti mkpu na agba asịrị n'etiti onwe ha

00:02:00.504 --> 00:02:03.320
Otu m siri mebie
agburu anyi niile.

00:02:04.540 --> 00:02:06.180
Aga m abụ onye a kpọrọ asị.

00:02:06.820 --> 00:02:10.060
"Gaba," e jiri m nwayọ
takwunyere ụgbọ njem

00:02:10.180 --> 00:02:11.255
na-azọsi ụkwụ m ike.

00:02:11.655 --> 00:02:15.056
ola mgbanụkwụ m yi
na nkwonkwo ụkwụ m abụọ yọgharịrị,

00:02:15.064 --> 00:02:16.680
mana a zọsiri m ụkwụ m ike ọzọ.

00:02:16.900 --> 00:02:20.520
Ọ nwere oge ụgbọ njem na arụkarịcha 
ọrụ mgbe m anaghị emetụ ya aka.

00:02:20.700 --> 00:02:24.036
"Gaba," ka m kwuru ọzọ,
ọsụsọ ana apụta m n'ihu isi.

00:02:24.256 --> 00:02:26.020
Oge n'onweghi ịhe megharịrị,

00:02:26.104 --> 00:02:29.940
A kwara m nnukwu igbe abụọ
nọ n'elụ ogbe ike aka.